			  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="../index.html">Home</a> ¬ª <a href="../issues">Issue Areas</a> ¬ª <a href="carbon-capture-and-storage" class="active">Carbon Capture and Storage</a></div>				  
				<div id="left-sbm-top">
					<h1>Carbon Capture and Storage</h1>  
															        
					<div id="node-96" class="node node-issue_area">



  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <img  class="imagefield imagefield-field_image" width="200" height="120" alt="" src="../files/chinainfo/chinafaqs-ccs&#32;v1.0.png?1255722031" />        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p>CCS may be a crucial tool in mitigating climate change, allowing us to <em>capture and store</em> CO<sub>2</sub> underground rather than emitting into the atmosphere. How are Chinese business and government leaders working to develop this emerging technology?</p>
  </div>

  <div class="clear-block">
    <div class="meta">
        </div>

      </div>

</div>
