  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/advisory-press-call-chinas-new-leadership-confronting-energy-and-environmental-challenges">ADVISORY: Press Call on China‚Äôs New Leadership: Confronting Energy and Environmental Challenges</a></span>
