  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>As China continues its leadership transition next week at the National People‚Äôs Congress, many are wondering how the country will confront its pressing environmental, climate, and energy challenges. On Friday, March 1 at 9 a.m. EST, WRI‚Äôs ChinaFAQs network will bring together leading experts for a press teleconference to discuss these issues.</p></div>
